INSERT {
  GRAPH narr:Tx_20260416T210000Z {
    narr:Narrative_CreativeCounterweightToAswritten skos:note "Aswritten demands speed and pragmatism ('dumber and faster'). The generative 3D project provides breathing room and a space for purely creative work unconstrained by business velocity. Clarified 2026-04-16: this is not a dead-end art project — it is an art project that might also be a real product if it keeps going. The process minimalism stance still applies, but the vision now includes a plausible product trajectory (live NRT-to-modular bridge)." .
  }
}
