INSERT {
  GRAPH narr:Tx_20260416T210000Z {
    narr:Narrative_TaylorCreativeIntersection skos:note "Not a formal shared project, but Scarlet wants a world of overlap where she can help Taylor with CAD and find creative intersection organically. Taylor is self-sufficient with the printer but has not yet done 3D modeling. Extended 2026-04-16: if the live NRT-to-modular bridge hardware packaging happens, this becomes a physical object that could be designed/CAD'd — a custom enclosure or module faceplate — creating natural overlap with Taylor's generative 3D interests. The modular context is already Scarlet's world; the CAD becomes a shared surface." .
  }
}
